	Eliminated name space checking.

	* pldap.el: New module.
	toplevel: Changed condition to detect built-in ldap feature.
	(ldap-delete): Enclosed call-process with `with-temp-buffer'.
	(ldap-add): Added error handling.
	(ldap-modify): Ditto.
	(ldap-delete): Ditto.

